						<summary>

						<p>This records the gift of a cocoa-nut garden, 3 <hi rend="italic">mā</hi> in extent, to provide for one <hi rend="italic">kāśu</hi> per month for <hi rend="italic">śidāri</hi> fumigation during the 4 services in the day, and four <hi rend="italic">kāśu</hi> per year for the daily supply of sandal-paste, in the temple of Tiruchchēlur-Mahādēva at Rājakēsari-chaturvēdimaṅgalam, by <hi rend="bold">Pūdi (Bhūti) Pallavappēraiyaṉ</hi> <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> <hi rend="bold">Vīrāśikhāmaṇi-Pallavaraiyaṉ.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
					</msContents>
